<tr id="L116"><td><a href="#L116">116</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Why didn't you say something earlier?</td></tr>

<tr id="L117"><td><a href="#L117">117</a></td><td>GUIDE:  Shall we get started?</td></tr>

<tr id="L118"><td><a href="#L118">118</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: She leads Janeway down the tunnels. Two young women approach and touch Janeway's hair.</td></tr>

<tr id="L119"><td><a href="#L119">119</a></td><td>GUIDE:  It's all right, Kathryn.</td></tr>

<tr id="L120"><td><a href="#L120">120</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Janeway allows them to unpin her bun and remove her uniform. Once she is naked, they paint designs on her face and body, then put a simple brown robe on her.</td></tr>

<tr id="L121"><td><a href="#L121">121</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Would it be breaking any vows of secrecy now to tell me what this ritual will involve?</td></tr>

<tr id="L122"><td><a href="#L122">122</a></td><td>GUIDE:  why do you think I know?</td></tr>

<tr id="L123"><td><a href="#L123">123</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Haven't you been through this before?</td></tr>

<tr id="L124"><td><a href="#L124">124</a></td><td>GUIDE:  Don't worry, I'll help you find your way. Tell me, have you completely committed yourself to this journey?</td></tr>

<tr id="L125"><td><a href="#L125">125</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Yes.</td></tr>

<tr id="L126"><td><a href="#L126">126</a></td><td>GUIDE:  You're willing to go through what the monks have been doing for centuries to help them find the spirits?</td></tr>

<tr id="L127"><td><a href="#L127">127</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Yes.</td></tr>

<tr id="L128"><td><a href="#L128">128</a></td><td>GUIDE:  So you can send biochemical data back to you ship. No, it wasn't magic. Our bioscanners detected the microprobe under your skin.</td></tr>

<tr id="L129"><td><a href="#L129">129</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  I hope that won't be a problem.</td></tr>

<tr id="L130"><td><a href="#L130">130</a></td><td>GUIDE:  Makes no difference at all. You are fond of your little devices, aren't you.</td></tr>

<tr id="L131"><td><a href="#L131">131</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  They've always served me well.</td></tr>

<tr id="L132"><td><a href="#L132">132</a></td><td>GUIDE:  I'm sure they have. Please, come this way.</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Waiting Room</td></tr>
<tr id="L133"><td><a href="#L133">133</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: There are pensioners sitting on a bench by the wall.</td></tr>

<tr id="L134"><td><a href="#L134">134</a></td><td>OLD MAN 1:  Who are you?</td></tr>

<tr id="L135"><td><a href="#L135">135</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  I'm Kathryn Janeway. Is this where the ritual begins?</td></tr>

<tr id="L136"><td><a href="#L136">136</a></td><td>OLD MAN 2:  Oh, the ritual. Yes.</td></tr>

<tr id="L137"><td><a href="#L137">137</a></td><td>OLD WOMAN:  We're waiting. Come, join us.</td></tr>

<tr id="L138"><td><a href="#L138">138</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  What exactly are you waiting for?</td></tr>

<tr id="L139"><td><a href="#L139">139</a></td><td>OLD MAN 2:  Just waiting.</td></tr>

<tr id="L140"><td><a href="#L140">140</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  How long have you been sitting here?</td></tr>

<tr id="L141"><td><a href="#L141">141</a></td><td>OLD MAN 2:  How long has it been?</td></tr>

<tr id="L142"><td><a href="#L142">142</a></td><td>OLD MAN 1:  Why are your asking me? I've lost track.</td></tr>

<tr id="L143"><td><a href="#L143">143</a></td><td>OLD MAN 2:  It's been a while. I know that.</td></tr>

